            <title>[CASSANDRA-16008] 2.2.17 fails to start up with ExceptionInInitializerError</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16008</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
